<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Laptop Shop</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="~/backend/css/grid.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        /* Section About Us */
        .about-us {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

            .about-us .row {
                display: flex;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                margin: 0;
            }

            .about-us .col {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .about-us .img-responsive {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 500px;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 12px;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            }

                .about-us .img-responsive:hover {
                    transform: scale(1.05);
                }

            .about-us ul {
                list-style: none;
                padding: 0;
                margin: 20px 0;
                text-align: left;
            }

                .about-us ul li {
                    font-size: 18px;
                    margin-bottom: 15px;
                    color: #333;
                }

        /* Testimonials Section */
        .testimonials-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .testimonials-section h2 {
                font-size: 36px;
                color: #333;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

            .testimonials-section blockquote {
                font-size: 20px;
                font-style: italic;
                border-left: 5px solid #ff6600;
                padding-left: 20px;
                margin: 30px;
                background: #fff;
                box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                position: relative;
                transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            }

                .testimonials-section blockquote:hover {
                    transform: translateY(-10px);
                }

            .testimonials-section cite {
                display: block;
                margin-top: 15px;
                font-size: 16px;
                color: #555;
            }

            .testimonials-section img {
                width: 60px;
                height: 60px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                margin-right: 10px;
                vertical-align: middle;
            }

        /* Sponsors Section */
        .sponsors-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background-color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .sponsors-section h2 {
                font-size: 36px;
                color: #333;
                margin-bottom: 40px;
            }

        .sponsor-showcase {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

            .sponsor-showcase li {
                margin: 20px;
                text-align: center;
                transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            }

                .sponsor-showcase li:hover {
                    transform: scale(1.1);
                }

            .sponsor-showcase img {
                width: 200px;
                height: auto;
                display: block;
                margin: 0 auto;
                transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            }

                .sponsor-showcase img:hover {
                    transform: scale(1.1);
                }

            .sponsor-showcase figcaption {
                font-size: 18px;
                color: #555;
                margin-top: 10px;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <section class="about-us">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col span-2-of-4">
                <img class="img-responsive" src="https://duhochopdiem.edu.vn/vnt_upload/study/15_09_2020/UEF4.jpg" alt="Laptop Shop">
            </div>
            <div class="col span-2-of-4">
                <ul>
                    <li>Cơ sở của shop tọa lạc tại địa chỉ 141 Điện Biên Phủ, TPHCM.</li>
                    <li>Được thành lập vào ngày 20/6/2024</li>
                    <li>Website bán laptop được xây dựng với mục tiêu cung cấp cho khách hàng một kênh mua sắm laptop uy tín, chất lượng và tiện lợi. Website sẽ mang đến cho khách hàng đa dạng các dòng laptop từ các thương hiệu nổi tiếng trên thế giới, đi kèm với giá cả cạnh tranh và dịch vụ chăm sóc khách hàng chu đáo.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
    <section class="testimonials-section" id="testimonials">
        <h2>Our Team Members</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col span-1-of-2">
                <blockquote>
                    Tien loi la uu tien hang dau
                    <cite>
                        <img src="~/backend/Images/person7.jpg" alt="person1">Dang Du Long 
                    </cite>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
            <div class="col span-1-of-2">
                <blockquote>
                    Nhanh Gon le
                    <cite>
                        <img src="~/backend/Images/person8.png" alt="person2"> Ngo Huu Vinh
                    </cite>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sponsors Section -->
    <section class="sponsors-section" id="sponsors">
        <h2>Our Sponsors</h2>
        <ul class="sponsor-showcase">
            <li>
                <figure>
                    <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTxa3QMtDRu-7pp2pcCF3MVk_X1ZBGe0euGJw&s" alt="msi">
                    <figcaption>MSI</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </li>
            <li>
                <figure>
                    <img src="https://logowik.com/content/uploads/images/apple8110.logowik.com.webp" alt="apple">
                    <figcaption>Apple</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </li>
            <li>
                <figure>
                    <img src="https://inkythuatso.com/uploads/thumbnails/800/2021/11/logo-acer-inkythuatso-2-01-27-15-50-00.jpg" alt="acer">
                    <figcaption>ACER</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.js" integrity="sha256-eKhayi8LEQwp4NKxN+CfCh+3qOVUtJn3QNZ0TciWLP4=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="~/backend/js/jquery.waypoints.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/backend/js/scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
